3icons.name: 3 Icons (Temporary)
3icons.description: Makes a three-icon code and keeps it in store for 24 hours, after which sequences may be reused.

14icons.name: 14 icons
14icons.description: Makes 14 icons from each three character group in the fingerprint.

liang.name: Liang Hashing
liang.description: Makes three progressively longer sequences to be checked so that faiures are spotted sooner.
